name: Neotoma 1
notes:
Based on the IntCal13 calibration curve. Two separate Bacon age models were done. The first age model included all age controls; however, the fit for the surface core was poor. Ages from this age model were assigned to all samples ≥750 cm depth. The second age model incuded only the core top and lead-210 dates; these ages were assigned to depths 700-744 cm. 

Age Model 1 Bacon command line: Bacon('CREELBAY',thick=30,acc.mean=8,d.max=3077,depths.file=TRUE)

3077 #d.max
1 #d.by
1 #depths.file
NA #slump

4 #mem.strength
